doctype html
html(lang='en')
    head
        meta(charset="utf-8")
        meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,500,600,700")
        link(rel="stylesheet", href="style.css")

    body
        div.svg-sprite
            include ./assets/sprite/sprite-icons.svg
        div.wrapper
            header.header
                div.container.header__container
                    +logo({"class": "header__logo"})

                    +hamburger
                    +nav(
                        [
                            [
                                ["about", "#"],
                                ["services", "#"],
                                ["technologies", "#"],
                                ["careers", "#"],
                                ["contact", "#"]
                            ],
                            0
                        ],
                        {"class": "header__nav"}
                    )
            main.main
                section.promo
                    div.promo__left
                    div.promo__right
                    div.promo__caption
                        div.promo__greet
                            div.promo__letter
                                img(src="./assets/letters/h-mobile.svg")
                            div.promo__letter.promo__letter--i
                                picture
                                    source(media="(min-width: 768px)" srcset="./assets/letters/i-desktop.svg")
                                    img(src="./assets/letters/i-mobile.svg")
                        div.promo__text
                            h1.promo__title We are DarkShark!
                            p.promo__subtitle We create software for people and their business.
                section.about
                    div.container
                        div.about__firstly
                            div.about__titles
                                +section-title(["about", "us"])
                            div.about__content
                                p After graduating with a degree in IT in 2008, our founder and CIO was met with a terrible job market. Unable to find a job, he realized that his true passion was for helping organizations with their technology. And from that passion, ItCon was born. After being in business a short time, he realized that many companies were being underserved and were constantly “putting out technology fires” that never should have happened in the first place.
